              <strong>Deep Code Generation &amp; Legacy Refactoring:</strong> Inside engineering organizations, GPT-5.6 accelerates software delivery by assisting developers in unit test generation, database schema migration, and refactoring legacy monoliths into clean, modular TypeScript and Node.js microservices.
            </li>
